data.description: Highly sought after Progresso neighborhood in Ft Lauderdale. Fabulous starter home  Great curb appeal. Large backyard w plenty of room for addition or pool.  Newly painted inside and outside.  AC repair 2021. Beautiful terrazzo flooring, new wood laminate in the 3rd bedroom which can also be used as a den. Has 2 French doors.  This is a gem and the cheapest house in Progresso. W/D hook up. Best Value in town!
